data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5 BR, 4 Bath home nestled in the serene Eagles Bluff neighborhood, near scenic walking and biking trails leading to downtown Hastings and Spring Lake Park where you can observe a herd of Bison roaming. This home offers convenient access to the cities. The 2-story foyer welcomes you with a large open floor plan and a flex room to the front of the home. The main level boasts a spacious kitchen loaded with cabinets including a butlers pantry, light filled corner sink and dining room leading to a deck overlooking the backyard with mature trees. The kitchen seamlessly connects to the family room with a cozy gas fireplace. The luxurious owner's en-suite features vaulted ceilings, large walk-in closet and a spacious bath with tub and separate tile shower. The lower level includes a 5th BR, 4th bath, workout room, large family room with gas fireplace and a kitchenette – great space for guests or grandparents. A perfect blend of comfort, convenience & natural beauty.
